    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1">Error XS9078</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal">All elements of a string concatenation must be of type &apos;string&apos;. Element {0} is of type &apos;{1}&apos;</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">Previous version of the X# compiler (just like C#) allowed you to do a string concatenation of non string values. This has been disabled now.</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
